<source>It helps you intuitively understand the plant's scheduling policies and operation logic through multi-dimensional data analysis.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="3">It helps you intuitively understand the plant's scheduling policies and operation logic through multi-dimensional data analysis.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="3">Deze helpt u om via multidimensionale gegevensanalyse op intuïtieve wijze inzicht te krijgen in het planningsbeleid en de bedrijfslogica van de installatie.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="3"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">fNRNtsMYd1+IJu2JCINjb19DbQQ=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="769bbcb9-29df-47fe-acaf-929aee0a3b79"><source>The main functions are as follows:</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="4">The main functions are as follows:</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="4">Dit zijn de belangrijkste functies:</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="4"><sdl:rep id="LtuvXZNn/Q6dLLzUFkDj+abB6Vw=" /><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">LtuvXZNn/Q6dLLzUFkDj+abB6Vw=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="245c5f30-070d-45d0-8349-be5381c91547"><source>Operating mode interpretation</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="5">Operating mode interpretation</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="5">Bedrijfsmodus</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="5"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">5t4JAj9CaJXfx9cTyt9NHGwg2vQ=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="8e72495a-26e4-4c4c-ab26-8f44a2056cc3"><source>Analyzes the energy consumption/generation curves, battery charge and discharge status, and grid transaction data in real time.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="6">Analyzes the energy consumption/generation curves, battery charge and discharge status, and grid transaction data in real time.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="6">Analyseert in realtime de curves van energieverbruik/-opwekking, de laad- en ontlaadstatus van de batterij en de nettransactiegegevens.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="6"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">MH7foRYdWp+OBPFMXm/O0+ORxSA=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="713e9962-4bef-4166-bbbf-d828486dc69d"><source>Intelligently analyzes the economic and reliability considerations of the current scheduling policy.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="7">Intelligently analyzes the economic and reliability considerations of the current scheduling policy.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="7">Analyseert op intelligente wijze de economische en betrouwbaarheidsoverwegingen van het huidige planningsbeleid.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="7"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">9RL6Fsit+xebmw3dulhGHxhXCzA=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="bca7c852-26ee-4c5e-9ff0-9dc5b20f3b66"><source>Device behavior clarification</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="8">Device behavior clarification</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="8">Verduidelijking van apparaatgedrag</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="8"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">BLPyIz1vzxV3eqRL55AxXX51wHQ=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="10efc965-534a-4cea-ac10-56cd02dfb226"><source>Explains the trigger conditions and optimization objectives for charge and discharge actions of batteries.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="9">Explains the trigger conditions and optimization objectives for charge and discharge actions of batteries.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="9">Legt de activeringsvoorwaarden en optimalisatiedoelstellingen voor laad- en ontlaadhandelingen van batterijen uit.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="9"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">DeIqXv61uMPESSc7zhNmrE1CgOY=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="3d564911-08cc-4ea2-8c2a-961d57e7ebad"><source>Allows you to query the basis for the operating policy during a specified period.</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="10">Allows you to query the basis for the operating policy during a specified period.</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="10">Hiermee kunt u de basis voor het bedrijfsbeleid tijdens een opgegeven periode opvragen.</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="10"><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">XBfzBtTlTGL8TMSvuEeyzsFnvoY=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="2cb289e9-f1cd-4922-9dfa-b56c163ab05e"><source>Applicable Scope</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="11">Applicable Scope</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="11">Toepassingsbereik</mrk></target><sdl:seg-defs><sdl:seg id="11"><sdl:rep id="CCDv9AlU7ZvlZOApOYiqdZnQkxU=" /><sdl:value key="SegmentIdentityHash">CCDv9AlU7ZvlZOApOYiqdZnQkxU=</sdl:value></sdl:seg></sdl:seg-defs></trans-unit></group><group><sdl:cxts><sdl:cxt id="1" /><sdl:cxt id="2" /><sdl:cxt id="3" /></sdl:cxts><trans-unit id="9dcc4888-cedd-4424-8262-aaa64109fdf9"><source><g id="3">Plant type</g>:</source><seg-source><mrk mtype="seg" mid="12"><g id="3">Plant type</g>:</mrk></seg-source><target><mrk mtype="seg" mid="12"><g id="3">Type installatie</g>:</mrk></target><sdl:se